ActNational Capital Act
Financial Administration Act
SubjectFederal real property located at the Sir John Carling Site ** Transfer **
PrecisOrder transferring the administration of the federal real property located at the Sir John Carling Site from the Minister of Agriculture and Agri-Food to the Minister of Public Services and Procurement and the transfer of title from the National Capital Commission to Her Majesty the Queen in Right of Canada as represented by the Minister of Public Services and the Minister of Public Services and Procurement at a nominal value.
